+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
+					pktgen_app							+
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

1. An User space Application, which is used to generate the packets 
	from user space application.
2. The destination address and the mode of transfer are configurable.
	The idea is to implement the light weight packet generation 
	application and which can utilize the full link/speed of the network card.
3. The code designed for x86 platform and can be easily ported to embedded platforms.

